\c 5
\s Kubatwa kwehove zhinji
\p
\v 1 Zvino zvakaitika kuti vanhu vazhinji vakati vachimumbandidzira kuti vanzwe shoko raMwari, iye akamira parutivi rwegungwa reGenesareti;
\v 2 akaona zvikepe zviviri zvimire parutivi rwegungwa; asi vabati vehove vakanga vabuda mazviri vachisuka mimbure.
\v 3 Akapinda mune chimwe chikepe chaiva chaSimoni, akakumbira kwaari kuti abve pamhenderekedzo zvishoma. Zvino akagara, akadzidzisa chaunga ari muchikepe.
\p
\v 4 Wakati apedza kutaura, akati kuna Simoni: Pinda kwakadzika ukande mimbure yenyu kuti ubate.
\v 5 Simoni akapindura, akati kwaari: Tenzi, tabhindauka usiku hwose, tikasabata chinhu, asi zvamadaro imwi, ndichadzikisa mumbure.
\v 6 Vakati vaita izvozvo, vakakomba dutu rehove zhinji; mimbure yavo ikange yobvaruka.
\v 7 Vakaninira vamwe \add vavo\add* vakanga vari mune chimwe chikepe, kuti vauye kuzovabatsira; vakauya vakazadza zvikepe zvose zviri zviviri, zvokuti zvakatanga kunyura.
\v 8 Zvino Simoni Petro wakati achiona, akawira pasi pamabvi aJesu, akati: Ibvai kwandiri, Ishe, nokuti ndiri munhu mutadzi.
\v 9 Nokuti wakanga abatwa nokushamiswa, iye navose vaakanga anavo nokubatwa kwehove dzavakanga vabata;
\v 10 saizvozvovo Jakobho naJohwani, vanakomana vaZebedhi, vaiva pamwechete naSimoni. Ipapo Jesu akati kuna Simoni: Usatya, kubva zvino uchabata vanhu.
\v 11 Zvino, vakati vaisa zvikepe kunyika, vakasiya zvose vakamutevera.
\s Jesu unoporesa munhu unamaperembudzi
\p
\v 12 Zvino zvakaitika, ari kune rimwe guta, tarira, murume wakanga azere maperembudzi; wakati achiona Jesu akawa nechiso, ndokumukumbira, achiti: Ishe, kana muchida, munogona kundinatsa.
\v 13 Ipapo akatambanudza ruvoko, akamubata, achiti: Ndinoda, chinatswa. Pakarepo maperembudzi akabva kwaari.
\v 14 Akamuraira kuti asaudza munhu; \add akati\add*: Asi enda undozviratidza kumupristi, ubayire pamusoro pakunatswa kwako, sezvakarairwa naMozisi, chive chapupu kwavari.
\v 15 Asi mukurumbira wake wakanyanya kupararira kose; zvaunga zvikuru zvikaungana kuzomunzwa, nokuporeswa naye matenda avo.
\v 16 Asi iye waienda kunzvimbo dzerenje achinoyengetera.
\s Jesu unoporesa munhu wakawoma mitezo
\p
\v 17 Zvino zvakaitika nerimwe ramazuva, iye wakanga achidzidzisa; zvino vaFarisi navadzidzisi vomurairo vakanga vagerepo, vaibva kumisha yose yeGarirea neJudhiya neJerusarema; nesimba raShe rakanga riri\add po\add* kuvaporesa.
\v 18 Zvino tarira, varume vakanga vakatakura munhu panhovo wakanga akawoma mitezo; vakatsvaka kumupinza vamuise pamberi pake.
\v 19 Zvino, vakati vachishaiwa pavangamupinza napo, nokuda kwechaunga, vakakwira pamusoro peimba, vakamuburusira mukati nenhovo \add yake\add*, pamapfuriro pakati pamberi paJesu.
\v 20 Iye wakati aona kutenda kwavo, akati kwaari: Murume, zvivi zvako wazvikangamwirwa.
\v 21 Zvino vanyori navaFarisi vakatanga kufunga, vachiti: Ndianiko uyu unotaura achimhura Mwari? Ndianiko ungakangamwira zvivi, kunze kwaMwari oga?
\v 22 Zvino Jesu, paakaziva mifungo yavo, akapindura, akati kwavari: Munofungeiko mumoyo yenyu?
\v 23 Chinyiko chakareruka, kuti: Zvivi zvako wazviregererwa; kana kuti: Simuka, ufambe?
\v 24 Asi kuti muzive kuti Mwanakomana womunhu unesimba panyika rokuregerera zvivi, (akati kunowairwara nokuwoma mitezo): Ndinoti kwauri: Simuka, utore nhovo yako, uende kumba kwako.
\v 25 Pakarepo akasimuka pamberi pavo, akatora chaakanga avete pamusoro pacho, akaenda kumba kwake, achirumbidza Mwari.
\v 26 Kushamisika kukabata vose, vakarumbidza Mwari, vakazadzwa nokutya, vachiti: Taona chisionekwe nhasi.
\s Kudamwa kwaRevhi
\p
\v 27 Zvino shure kwaizvozvo wakabuda, akaona muteresi, nezita \add wainzi\add* Revhi, agere paimba inotererwa, akati kwaari: Nditevere.
\v 28 Iye akasiya zvose, akasimuka akamutevera.
\v 29 Revhi akamuitira mutambo mukuru mumba make; kukavapo chaunga chikuru chavateresi navamwe vakanga vanavo pakudya.
\v 30 Asi vanyori vavo navaFarisi vakanyunyutira vadzidzi vake, vachiti: Nemhaka yei muchidya nokumwa navateresi navatadzi?
\v 31 Jesu akapindura akati kwavari: Vasingarwari havatsvaki murapi, asi avo vanorwara.
\v 32 Handina kuuya kuzodana vakarurama, asi vatadzi, vauye mukutendeuka.
\s Kutsanya
\p
\v 33 Zvino vakati kwaari: Nemhaka yei vadzidzi vaJohwani vachitsanya kazhinji, vachiita minyengetero, navavaFarisi vanodarovo, asi venyu vanodya nokumwa.
\v 34 Asi wakati kwavari: Mungatsanyisa vana veimba yomuchato chikomba chiri kwavari here?
\v 35 Asi mazuva achasvika, apo chikomba chichabviswa kwavari, zvino ipapo vachatsanya namazuva iwayo.
\p
\v 36 Akatauravo mufananidzo kwavari, \add akati\add*: Hakunomunhu unoisa chigamba chitsva panguvo sharu; kana zvakadaro naichovo chitsva chinobvarura, nechigamba chakabva \add panguvo\add* itsva hachipindirani nechisharu.
\v 37 Uye hakunomunhu unodira waini itsva muhombodo sharu; kana zvakadaro, waini itsva ichaparusa hombodo ikateuka, uye nehombodo dzikaparara.
\v 38 Asi waini itsva inofanira kuiswa muhombodo itsva zvose zvichengetedzeke.
\v 39 Uye hakuna munhu unoti kana amwa \add waini\add* sharu, pakarepo akashuva itsva; nokuti unoti: Sharu iri nani.
